  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个完整的 Passkey 注册流程图。核心参与者包括终端用户、浏览器、设备认证器（比如手机或安全密钥）、Passkeys API，还有我们自己的后端服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Browser",
        "Authenticator",
        "PasskeyAPI",
        "Backend"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到安全层级有区分——OAuth2 和 ZeroTrust 两种安全策略。是不是浏览器到 PasskeyAPI 的通信用 OAuth2，而涉及设备认证器的敏感操作走 ZeroTrust？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Browser",
        "PasskeyAPI",
        "Authenticator"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这个理解准确。浏览器向后端和 PasskeyAPI 发起注册请求时用 OAuth2 令牌，但创建私钥凭证、生物识别验证这些环节必须走 ZeroTrust 通道。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "Browser",
        "Backend",
        "PasskeyAPI",
        "Authenticator"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程：用户点击注册按钮，浏览器向 PasskeyAPI 发送 POST /v1/signup/start 请求，API 内部生成挑战值后返回给浏览器，包含 rpID 和 userID。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Browser",
        "PasskeyAPI",
        "POST /v1/signup/start",
        "challenge",
        "rpID",
        "userID"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来是关键步骤——浏览器要调用设备认证器创建凭证，这里需要标注 ZeroTrust。然后认证器向用户弹出生物识别或 PIN 码提示，用户完成验证后凭证返回浏览器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Browser",
        "Authenticator",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "credential",
        "biometric",
        "PIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在浏览器拿着凭证 POST 到我们的后端 /signup 接口，后端先验证用户详情，再向 PasskeyAPI 发送 POST /v1/signup/finish 完成注册。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Browser",
        "Backend",
        "POST /signup",
        "POST /v1/signup/finish",
        "PasskeyAPI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，/v1/signup/finish 这个调用也要标记 ZeroTrust，因为涉及凭证的最终验证和存储。你刚才可能漏了安全标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "POST /v1/signup/finish",
        "Security_ZeroTrust",
        "PasskeyAPI",
        "credential"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，已补上 ZeroTrust 标注。流程收尾是 PasskeyAPI 返回验证结果，后端存储用户详情，然后浏览器向用户展示注册成功。",
